              "mode": "normal",
              "text": "The aims of the Government Industrial School / Secure Residential Facility (GIS/SRF) are to accommodate children, ordered to be resident therein, in a safe, secure, and caring environment, to address the children's rehabilitative needs, support the children's families to address the needs of their child, and work to reintegrate children into the community.",
